title: Studio with a View
posting_body: ['This lovely community is centrally located in Renton to provide easy access to both work and play throughout the city and surrounding area.', 'Each exquisite home offers modern fixtures and fine finishes to fit every individual lifestyle, while still accommodating the ease of adding your own personal touches throughout your new home.', 'You’ll find a wonderful array of amenities including 9 ft elevated ceilings, cozy living room fireplaces, and a fitness studio.', '-Located Near Lake Washington and  Cedar River Trail', '-In-home Washer & Dryer', '-Fitness Studio', '-Ample Storage, with Linen, Coat, & Large Bedroom Closets', '-Updated Stainless Steel Appliances', '-Additional Exterior Storage', '-Downtown Renton Views', '-Professional Caring Management Team', '-Flexible Rent Payment Options Available through <URL>', '-Terrace or Balcony', '-Onsite Recycling Bins', '-Courtesy Night Patrol', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices and Availability are Subject to Change Without Notice']
